{"tid":991370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為任正非：動不動就抓人 誰敢去投資？","createTime":"2019-01-22T10:36:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T02:07:52.000Z","uid":141151,"like":71,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"da78933cfb6502ccce02c9ceeebd9df170e5a185","tid":991370,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:36:41.000Z","msg":"<strong>華為任正非：動不動就抓人 誰敢到美國去投資？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2679168\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2679168&d=%2BsNn%2FKykQimad0B5M5gf%2FACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=4b9efcfb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2679168&h=7811efa0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2679168</a><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕華為風波持續延燒，在華為財務長孟晚舟在加拿大被逮，並恐引渡至美國，孟晚舟之父、創辦人任正非近期接受國際媒體採訪時直言：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「如果動不動就嚇唬一些國家，嚇唬一些公司，動不動就抓人，誰敢</span><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">到美國</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">去投資？」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n任正非15日接受國際媒體聯訪，華為則於21日公佈採訪紀要，根據紀要內容，任正非表示，他想透過媒體對美國說「合作共贏」，認為世界越來越高科技，越來越不可能由1個國家、1個公司完整地完成1件事情，與工業時代大不相同，任何1個市場機會都不可能由1家公司獨立完成，需要千萬個公司共同承擔。<br />\n<br />\n由於美國總統川普日前稱會考慮介入孟晚舟案，任正非表示，他目前也只能等著看，現在也無法做出判斷，但他也大讚川普是個偉大總統，敢大幅度減稅，認為減稅是有利投資。<br />\n<br />\n但任正非話鋒一轉，表示只有善待所有國家、善待所有公司，大家才會積極投資，投資產生的效益，才能把稅收減少彌補起來，「如果動不動就嚇唬一些國家，嚇唬一些公司，動不動就抓人，誰敢到美國去投資？」認為此舉會導致減稅創造的優越環境無法發揮作用。"},{"pid":"baf1fd29202edc17b79d31ff3d345cb2c70fc297","tid":991370,"uid":94828,"like":101,"dislike":0,"score":101,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:37:54.000Z","msg":"差啲睇唔到 到美國<br />\n以為佢講緊中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5cb6d9ccad5836cfc3eeed8ea1694ac87e03594","tid":991370,"uid":10757,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:38:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇錯 但同邊個國家講？某國投資到人都死埋"},{"pid":"1b3126624e54ce283ce970934d9047ac8471b84e","tid":991370,"uid":72228,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:39:36.000Z","msg":"華為又軍企底扮私企？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1543d0516f922efd76d05510f47996b1ebd2944","tid":991370,"uid":28765,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:39:59.000Z","msg":"唔係身有屎驚咩比人捉<br />\n<br />\n中國都係咁捉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9510a4ad904cbb3b9d61dfce111394bff88b2cf1","tid":991370,"uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"baf1fd29202edc17b79d31ff3d345cb2c70fc297","tid":991370,"uid":94828,"like":101,"dislike":0,"score":101,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:37:54.000Z","msg":"差啲睇唔到 到美國<br />\n以為佢講緊中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:40:12.000Z","msg":"x2"},{"pid":"955779d4ac810b6e791fa57c75c0efa0a7f0d136","tid":991370,"uid":43428,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:40:37.000Z","msg":"放心 淨係會捉中國人<br />\n至於點解...<br />\n你知我知大家知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117a1b7ddee33124c2e3f0a4a260e4cf0aba842a","tid":991370,"uid":44211,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:41:49.000Z","msg":"Cheng Lap : 指桑罵槐，習大大應該誅這種人九族，而且要用犬決。"},{"pid":"79cbe6b9df795f56ebf00b448daff1f18c50b5ec","tid":991370,"uid":65406,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:44:02.000Z","msg":"瘋了，一切都瘋了，有人將會被抑鬱"},{"pid":"de93e4e1d454830d0835c7178a5f37a13c836bdf","tid":991370,"uid":150347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:44:47.000Z","msg":"<img sr